Author  : Tak Tang   tst92@ecs.soton.ac.uk
Date    : 7/7/96

Introduction

    I wanted to create a trashcan which people can put rubish in,
rather like the garbage room, but as an object.  Yet again, this is
one of my earliest pieces of code, so dont give me grief over it! 
It is mostly built around the garbage room code.


Installation

    Log on as SysAdmin, source the file.  Create a child of the trashcan
object, and put it somewhere where people will use it.


