Other ramblings

    I guess you could offer a small "reward" for people being
tidy and throwing things away.  I noticed that CirclMUD has a "junk"
command which destroys unwanted objects, and gives you some money
in reward.  I might try to set up the trashcan as a recycling
thing, which rewards the players for clearing up.

